author: Nico Amarca
title: Tommy Genesis Drops New Line of “World Vision” Hoodies
text:
Previous Next 
It’s been a whole year since alt rap queen Tommy Genesis dropped her game-changing debut LP, World Vision . In light of the album’s success and Tommy’s rising notoriety in the spheres of music and fashion, the artist’s camp has decided to re-release a set of hoodies that were first made available when the album was initially released – seeing as only 30 of them were made. 
Available in black and white colorways, the hoodies feature World Vision ‘s Rorschach-esque cover art on the backside along with a title logo on the front.
